      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/573703130_18540232000052855_1091012180358367542_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc1OTM4Nzg5NTM0NzE0ODY5OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE5MjB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=WrdXx0WY6YYQ7kNvwFgonRw&amp;_nc_oc=AdoSJmpPO-bQyNlEw_HaeAnL3Q86upJ297vKu7xMibckxb0Diqz5ZIUHqDUWTBJF3gQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=BdR-26wa7EnoDkKQaK-7tQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxKC7eEAqgWxiyXH9coJcTjut7Noc6JQQ74_lkyBuYqAg&amp;oe=69C9C19C" alt="Instagram billede fra @trophysophie" /></p><p><strong>@trophysophie</strong></p><p>Tom Llamas invited Ronnie to be a culture correspondent on NBC News to talk about her favorite films and music! She is a total film buff. What a thrill!! Link in bio for the full segment. Thank you so much for having us and asking the hard-hitting questions @llamasnbc @topstorynbc :)</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/573703130_18540232000052855_1091012180358367542_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc1OTM4Nzg5NTM0NzE0ODY5OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE5MjB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=WrdXx0WY6YYQ7kNvwFgonRw&amp;_nc_oc=AdoSJmpPO-bQyNlEw_HaeAnL3Q86upJ297vKu7xMibckxb0Diqz5ZIUHqDUWTBJF3gQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=BdR-26wa7EnoDkKQaK-7tQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxKC7eEAqgWxiyXH9coJcTjut7Noc6JQQ74_lkyBuYqAg&amp;oe=69C9C19C" alt="Instagram billede fra @trophysophie" /></p><p><strong>@trophysophie</strong></p><p>Tom Llamas invited Ronnie to be a culture correspondent on NBC News to talk about her favorite films and music! She is a total film buff. What a thrill!! Link in bio for the full segment. Thank you so much for having us and asking the hard-hitting questions @llamasnbc @topstorynbc :)</p>]]></content:encoded>
