      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/559934024_18532750210052855_3079805532125299508_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=MzczNTUwMTc5NzIxODcxMjgzOQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=wo-0kX3LamUQ7kNvwG_cdnh&amp;_nc_oc=AdprSdzlvfEy4HyUjH3MaEtoFc6aOXiujCOEGRYv_dgKkkN9QT-JS8ER4Aodl-Pe_hI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=BdR-26wa7EnoDkKQaK-7tQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwnOS2s_rGfzDGHbBF1bJmEsJ039cKtxRp6jzFJ5hxf_w&amp;oe=69C9A051" alt="Instagram billede fra @trophysophie" /></p><p><strong>@trophysophie</strong></p><p>We were last weeks cover story for @nytimes Thursday Styles and still can’t believe it!!! Once again.. thank you for chatting with me @alexvadukul - there are also some really great Candice Bergen quotes in the piece which is an honor. And especially thank you to everyone who has ever supported me and come to see a show 🥜 <br/>
Ronnie still can’t believe this placement. She’s going to line the inside of her trunk with them. <br/>
Photos by @dina_litovsky</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/559934024_18532750210052855_3079805532125299508_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=MzczNTUwMTc5NzIxODcxMjgzOQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=wo-0kX3LamUQ7kNvwG_cdnh&amp;_nc_oc=AdprSdzlvfEy4HyUjH3MaEtoFc6aOXiujCOEGRYv_dgKkkN9QT-JS8ER4Aodl-Pe_hI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=BdR-26wa7EnoDkKQaK-7tQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwnOS2s_rGfzDGHbBF1bJmEsJ039cKtxRp6jzFJ5hxf_w&amp;oe=69C9A051" alt="Instagram billede fra @trophysophie" /></p><p><strong>@trophysophie</strong></p><p>We were last weeks cover story for @nytimes Thursday Styles and still can’t believe it!!! Once again.. thank you for chatting with me @alexvadukul - there are also some really great Candice Bergen quotes in the piece which is an honor. And especially thank you to everyone who has ever supported me and come to see a show 🥜 <br/>
Ronnie still can’t believe this placement. She’s going to line the inside of her trunk with them. <br/>
Photos by @dina_litovsky</p>]]></content:encoded>
